	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/2622/">#2622</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/08/29 10:12 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/08/29 10:12 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/commonlisp/">
	  Common Lisp
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'>REPLと二人三脚で作りました。</pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8
9</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>(defun pyramid (str)
  (let ((base (coerce (cdr (reduce (lambda (r x) `(,@r #\Space ,x))
				   (coerce str &#39;list)
				   :initial-value &#39;())) &#39;string)))
    (do ((idx 2 (+ idx 2))
	 (len (length base))
	 (result base (concatenate &#39;string spacer (subseq base idx) &quot;~%&quot; result))
	 (spacer &quot; &quot; (concatenate &#39;string &quot; &quot; spacer)))
	((&gt; idx len) (format t result)))))
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
