<div class="comment" id="comment2654">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/59/" target="_top">nori</a><a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100605050114im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_silver.png" border=0/></a><a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100605050114im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/2654/">#2654</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/08/30 01:02 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/08/30 01:02 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/python/">
	  Python
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'>デフォルト引数を使って単独の関数で再帰実装。

最下段の取り扱いが納得いかない。
全部returnで書きたいのだが・・・。

長さ0文字の文字列には対応しておりません。
</pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre> 1
