<div class="comment" id="comment4001">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/4/" target="_top">匿名</a><a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100605050114im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_gold.png" border=0/></a><a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100605050114im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/4001/">#4001</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/11/14 10:04 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/11/14 10:04 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20100605050114/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/nadesico/">
	  なでしこ
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'></pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8
9</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>「abracadabra」のピラミッドを表示
●ピラミッド(sの)
    tとは配列
    ケタ数=(2*バイト数(s)-1)
    (バイト数(s))回
        tに(文字列センタリング(文字列注入(RIGHT(s,回数),&quot; &quot;),ケタ数))を配列追加
    tで戻る
●文字列注入(sにlを)
    sを文字列分解してlで配列結合で戻る
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
  <div align = "right" class="banner">
	
